 privacy of all its service recipients as well as <strong>Users<\/strong> of its website located at <a href=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/\">https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/<\/a>&nbsp; (\u201c<strong>Site<\/strong>\u201d). This privacy policy (\u201c<strong>Policy<\/strong>\u201d) discloses the practices and policies adopted by <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> for collecting, retrieving, possessing, storing, dealing, handling, or using personal data and sensitive personal data or information it may receive from any person who avails services of <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> or accesses or uses the <strong>Site<\/strong> (\u201c<strong>User\/Users<\/strong>\u201d). All terms and conditions of the use of the <strong>Site<\/strong> are incorporated in this Policy by reference. The Policy seeks to comply with the Information Technology Act, 2000 (\u201cAct\u201d), the Information Technology (Reasonable Security Practices and Procedures and Sensitive Personal Data or Information) Rules, 2011 (\u201cRules\u201d), and other applicable laws. Due consideration has also been given to privacy laws of jurisdictions all over the world, so as to ensure that this <strong>Policy<\/strong> is up to date with evolving laws throughout the world.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>This <strong>Policy<\/strong> is binding on all levels of <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> including employees, and any other persons authorized by it to collect, process, or use data. The <strong>Policy<\/strong> will cover all data, including any confidential information, obtained from all <strong>Users<\/strong> and any other person whose data is consensually provided to <strong>Rivermist<\/strong>, except anonymized data or any data that is freely available in the public domain. <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> reserves the right to modify and update this <strong>Policy<\/strong> to keep up with changing legal landscape and other legal regulations that it might be bound by in the future. <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> reserves the right to add, modify, update, or delete any part of this <strong>Policy<\/strong> as it deems fit without giving notice. <strong>Users<\/strong> are encouraged to periodically check the <strong>Policy<\/strong> to see any such additions, modifications, updates, or deletions.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>1. DEFINITIONS<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<p>The terms used in this <strong>Policy<\/strong> would mean and be interpreted as defined in the Information Technology Act, 2000, and the Information Technology (Reasonable Security Practices and Procedures and Sensitive Personal Data or Information) Rules, 2011 unless defined elsewhere in this <strong>Policy<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>&#8220;Applicable Law&#8221; means all applicable statutes, acts of Indian legislature, ordinances, rules, bye-laws, guidelines, regulations, directions, directives, notifications, circulars, policies, and orders of any government, statutory authority, regulatory authority, tribunal, board or court in India;<\/li>\n<li>&#8220;General Information&#8221; will have the same meaning ascribed to it in clause 2.5 of the <strong>Policy<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<li>&#8220;Personal Information&#8221; shall mean information disclosed by or obtained from any <strong>User<\/strong> and includes name, age, occupation, e-mail, residential address, telephone number, payment processing details, and any other personal details capable of identifying such a person.<\/li>\n<li>&#8220;Sensitive Personal Information&#8221; shall, excluding any information that is freely available or accessible in the public domain or is furnished under Applicable Laws, mean the following information: account password, physical, physiological or mental health condition, sexual orientation; medical records, and history; financial information such as bank account or credit\/debit card details or other payment instruction details.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3>2. <strong>INFORMATION COLLECTION THROUGH THE SITE <\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>A <strong>User<\/strong> might be required to disclose Personal Information (including Sensitive Personal Information) while browsing through the <strong>Site<\/strong> or for availing <strong>Rivermist\u2019s<\/strong> Such information might be collected by various online and offline methods such as filling forms, questionnaires, surveys, chatbots<span style=\"color: #808000;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">,<\/span>&nbsp;<\/span>documents provided, and other modes of contacting <strong>Rivermist<\/strong>. This further includes information collected by guests who stay at <strong>Rivermist Resorts<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<li>Prior to providing Personal Information to <strong>Rivermist<\/strong>, a <strong>User<\/strong> must grant consent to Rivermist for using the Personal Information. By use of the <strong>Site or Rivermist\u2019s Services<\/strong>, <strong>Users<\/strong> agree that they are consensually providing information in accordance with this <strong>Policy<\/strong>. The Personal Information will be used only for the purposes set out in clause 4 of the <strong>Policy<\/strong>.&nbsp;If the <strong>User<\/strong> does not wish to provide such Personal Information, the <strong>User<\/strong> must not proceed with using the <strong>Site<\/strong> or availing <strong>Rivermist\u2019s<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Rivermist<\/strong> will collect Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information only for a lawful purpose connected with a function or activity of <strong>Rivermist<\/strong>, for which activity the Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information is reasonably considered necessary.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Rivermist<\/strong> will not be responsible for the correctness or completeness of the Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information provided by the <strong>User<\/strong>, or any consequences arising in relation to incorrect or incomplete Personal Information or Sensitive Information.<\/li>\n<li>While browsing through the <strong>Site<\/strong>, the <strong>Site<\/strong> server may automatically record some general information about the <strong>User\u2019s<\/strong> visit, including but not limited to the date and time of visiting the <strong>Site<\/strong>, the type of browser being used, etc. (\u201cGeneral Information\u201d). Such General Information collected is not Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information for the purpose of this Policy.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Rivermist<\/strong> reserves the right to use General Information collected by it for any purpose whatsoever including tracking overall traffic patterns, statistical analysis, and marketing and promotional purposes. Consequently, <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> may share such General Information or any analysis with any third party, at its discretion.<\/li>\n<li>Subject to the provisions of this <strong>Policy<\/strong>, any other agreements entered into, or laws in force, <strong>Users<\/strong> shall have the rights of access; updation and correction; and deletion of their data. <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> shall endeavor to provide easy and free access, through online and offline modes, to a copy of data, unless it is deemed to be a frivolous\/vexatious request, jeopardizes the privacy of other <strong>Users<\/strong>, or for which access is not otherwise required by local law. <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> may also decline to give access to, modify, or delete any data if it believes that such requests shall undermine the legitimate use of the data for anti-fraud\/security purposes or that such data might be required by governments or legal authorities in the due exercise of their powers.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3>3. USE OF PERSONAL INFORMATION AND SENSITIVE PERSONAL INFORMATION<\/h3>\n<p>By using the <strong>Site<\/strong> or availing of <strong>Rivermist\u2019s<\/strong> Services, a <strong>User<\/strong> consents to the collection and use of Personal information by <strong>Rivermist<\/strong>. Personal Information disclosed to <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> by a <strong>User<\/strong> may be used by <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> for any clear and lawful purpose including one or more of the following purposes:<\/p>\n<p>(a)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; in creating content that is relevant to the <strong>User<\/strong>;<\/p>\n<p>(b)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; in improving the content of the <strong>Site<\/strong>;<\/p>\n<p>(b)&nbsp; to maintain a database of all the Personal Information collected from the <strong>User<\/strong>;<\/p>\n<p>(c)&nbsp; to evaluate and administer the <strong>Site<\/strong> and resolve any problems that may arise with the usage of the <strong>Site<\/strong>;<\/p>\n<p>(d) to improve order processing and order confirmations;<\/p>\n<p>(e) to respond to <strong>User<\/strong> inquiries and feedback;<\/p>\n<p>(f) to use the information to notify <strong>Users<\/strong> about important functionality changes to the <strong>Site<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><!-- \/wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --><\/p>\n<h3><strong>4. INFORMATION SHARING AND DISCLOSURE OF PERSONAL INFORMATION AND SENSITIVE PERSONAL INFORMATION<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Only Persons authorized by <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> shall have access to Personal Information and Sensitive Personal Information disclosed to Rivermist. <strong>User<\/strong> grants consent to <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> for sharing Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information with persons who are associated with<\/li>\n<li>Notwithstanding anything contained in this Policy, <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> reserves the right to disclose any Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information that may be required to be disclosed under applicable law or to any governmental authority or to a Court of Law, without prior notice or consent of the <strong>User<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3><strong>5. DISCLOSURE TO THIRD PARTY<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>In case the information is being collected and retained by a third party, on behalf of <strong>Rivermist<\/strong>, <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> shall endeavor to give reasonable notice to the <strong>User<\/strong> before the transfer of information to any third party unless such disclosure is necessary for compliance with a legal obligation. Such obligation is also not applicable in a case such information is being transferred to a government agency when a request for such transfer has been made by such government agency to <strong>Rivermist<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Rivermist<\/strong> may transfer Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information to any company or person located in India or any other country only if it is necessary for the performance of a lawful contract between <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> and any person, provided the same level of data protection will be adhered to by the other company. <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> cannot guarantee that such parties will keep the Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information confidential and <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> will not be liable in any manner for any loss of confidentiality attributable to such third parties.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3><strong>6. SECURITY<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Rivermist<\/strong> has taken all reasonable measures and precautions to keep the Personal Information and Sensitive Personal Information safe and secure and to prevent any unauthorized access to or misuse of the same.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Rivermist<\/strong> shall be liable to inform <strong>Users<\/strong>, within a reasonable time, of any misuse, modification, unauthorized access, disclosure, or destruction of any data it has obtained. <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> shall take further steps to minimize the harm caused due to any such activity, including legal steps.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3><strong>7. LIABILITY<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><strong>Rivermist<\/strong> shall not be liable to any <strong>User<\/strong> for any loss, damage (whether direct, indirect, consequential, or incidental), or harm caused to the <strong>User<\/strong> due to the unauthorized access or misuse of the Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Information by any third party beyond the control of <strong>Rivermist<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>In no event will <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> be liable for any damages whatsoever in an amount in excess of any purchase of service made by <strong>Users<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>8. LINKING TO OTHER SITES<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><strong>Rivermist<\/strong> is not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of any other websites for which links may be provided on the <strong>Site<\/strong>. By clicking on a link, logo, or other such items, or using certain services available on the <strong>Site<\/strong>, <strong>Users<\/strong> may no longer be on the <strong>Site<\/strong> and in such circumstances, the privacy policy of such other websites shall apply. <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> encourages <strong>Users<\/strong> to read the posted privacy statement of the other websites whenever interacting with any websites.<\/p>\n<h3>9. INDEMNIFICATION<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Users<\/strong> agree to defend, indemnify, and hold harmless <strong>Rivermist<\/strong> and its affiliates and their respective officers, employees, and agents from and against all claims and expenses, including attorneys&#8217; fees, arising out of the use of this <strong>Site<\/strong> by <strong>Users<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h3>10. GOVERNING LAW AND JURISDICTION<\/h3>\n<p>By visiting this <strong>Site<\/strong>, the <strong>User<\/strong> agrees that this Policy shall be construed in accordance with and be governed by the laws o